	(1826,687,'about_text','<h2 class=\"tax-ttile tax-title\">It’s a square… an (almost)</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"tax-ttile tax-title\"><span class=\"red\">regular square…</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a Square, but not a simple Square.\r\n</strong><strong>It’s a Square where almost everything is possible.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nUnicorns in magazine covers, Walking Libraries on cars\r\nWitch\'s Drool and Bone Cream on national tv.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis is a Square full of work, dedication and commitment.\r\nAnd also a Square full of creativity, proximity and joy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a Square, but not a simple Square.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a square because it was born in a square.\r\nIt’s a square because we want to prove that PR can be done with (almost) regular ideas, where storyteling make the difference.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a square, but not a simple square.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a square made of courage. Of willingness to win.\r\nOf a big desire to do more and better. Always.\r\nIt’s a square made for those who are not afraid to risk, to do, to create.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt’s a square to face the New Economy challenges where connecting and beeing social is crucial.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a square, but not a simple square.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>It’s a square opened to the future.</strong>'),
