	(1832,693,'about_text','<h2>It’s a square… an (almost)</h2>\r\n<h3>regular square…</h3>\r\nIt’s a Square, but not a simple Square. It’s a Square where almost everything is possible. Unicorns in magazine covers, Walking Libraries on cars, Witch\'s Drool and Bone Cream on national tv, Solidarity Lockers around the city… costumer experience is a must… This is a Square full of work, dedication and commitment. And also a Square full of creativity, proximity and joy. It’s a Square, but not a simple Square. For us, the sky is the limit, almost like an open square. It’s a Square because it was born in a square. It’s a Square because we want to prove that PR can be done with “(almost) regular ideas”, where the execution and storyteling make the difference, and with measurable impact. It’s a Square where PR, influence, digital and content marketing reign. We love content and storytelling.'),
