	(2993,838,'descricao','<span class=\"highlight\">From <strong>Cascais </strong>to The Square….</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\"><strong>Graduated in Communication Sciences &amp; Journalism from Universidade Autónoma de Lisboa</strong>. João’s teenage dream of becoming a war reporter was the propeller to his career in journalism. While studying, João had a podcast and a blog, both called Utópicos. He started his professional career as a journalist, where he closely followed the tech and entrepreneurial ecosystem in Portugal for two years.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\">João is always open to meet interesting people, especially entrepreneurs with insane ideas - Elon Musk, if you’re reading this, please do call him.</p>'),
