	(4004,960,'descricao','<span class=\"highlight\">From <strong>Caldas da Rainha</strong> to The Square….</span>\r\n\r\nHaving begun her professional career as a journalist and editor in health, human resources and tourism publications, Ana has since been acting as a senior specialist in renowned communication agencies for the past 15 years, following the trail initiated by her <strong>graduation in Communication, from Universidade Técnica de Lisboa</strong>. Along the way, she has also managed communications and marketing departments in a non-governmental organization for development, a national innovation institute, and a software house, before joining The Square´s multidisciplinary team.\r\n\r\nUpon completing 10 years as a piano student, her spare time is divided between her passions: art, travel and books.'),
