	(13,'\"quotes\"','{\"order\":{\"section_391ff660b\":{\"row_brqc20rk1\":{\"columns\":{\"column_a4addb2be\":[\"content_e84779b05\",\"content_987769f57\"]}},\"row_ym2iwjy6q\":{\"columns\":{\"column_3ha4y0byq\":[\"content_zaetcftua\"]}},\"row_v8mdftbyg\":{\"columns\":{\"column_gn0ykoaq9\":[\"content_td4d1dw5v\"]}},\"row_4taa1mv88\":{\"columns\":{\"column_qlnnlfkqz\":[\"content_aic2mbjik\"]}}}},\"section_391ff660b\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\",\"data-xs-visibility\":\"visbile\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\",\"padding-bottom\":\"5.555555555555555rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_a4addb2be\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_e84779b05\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.55556rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.55556rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">2017 finished and it was memorable…</span></p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">2017 finished and it was memorable…</span></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_987769f57\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">The worlds of fashion and housing crowdfunding were love at first sight and the beginning of a lifelong journey, we hope. On the way, we also gave a ride to our friend Zé Francisco and we did a “pit stop” at Portugal’s most disruptive agency that frequently provokes us to think outside the box. All this zigzagging requires the best protection, so at the end of this road, we did an accurate hat-trick in Viseu.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem; font-size: 1.11111rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem; font-size: 1.11111rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\">… and 2018 is already starting with<span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\"> great news.</span></span></p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">The Square is starting 2018 with new passengers onboard: from the banking sector to technology consulting, from mobility platforms to the restaurant of a duke… The Square intends to go further, but always with sustainability and by conquering the respect<span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\"> of the ones who choose us as drivers of their communication challenges. On our side, all we can do is to remain as committed and rigorous withou</span>t never losing our way and strict principles. &nbsp;</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">The hard work had already started on January 2nd.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Are you curious? We’ll tell you more in Behind The Square <span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\">#2.</span></p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">See you soon!</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">The Square Team</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem; font-size: 0.722222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;