":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_9f2ff001d\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_08655511a\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;November</span>, we got out of The Square to visit the Web Summit… &nbsp;</p>\",\"xs\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"font-size: 1.44444rem; line-height: 1.72222rem;\\\"><span class=\\\"font_pv7ryu5ou\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(246, 60, 59);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #f63c3b;\\\">In&nbsp;November,</span> we got out of The Square<span style=\\\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86);\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"color: #565656;\\\"> to visit the Web Summit… &nbsp;</span></span></p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_6bcb693e4\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">Entrepreneurial spirit and resilience to walk the path of stones are part of our DNA. So, we couldn’t miss the biggest conference on technology and entrepreneurship in the world.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">As we didn’t have the chance to take part in the meetings, we decided to stand out in a more creative way: we took The Square to the Web Summit. We took advantage of our PR capacities and showed to global startups and big companies what we do best: placing great companies and ideas on the most relevant media outlets.</p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\" data-mce-style=\\\"line-height: 1.27778rem;\\\">We took a poster – bigger than us –and photographed 60 participants from several countries. We raise 60 news “squares” (i.e. visit cards) and schedule 10 meetings: mission accomplished.</p>\"},\"module\":\"paragraph\",\"options\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.1111111111111112rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_c76c6b9bf\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"12\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"1.6666666666666667rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_c7cac3c05\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":519},\"module\":\"image\",\"options\":{\"align\":\"center\"},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_wbou4f6c0\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"\"},\"module\":\"spacer\",\"options\":{\"height\":\"0.1111111111111111rem\",\"background-color\":\"#f63c3b\"},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_ebeiu9fr7\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"1\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"2.7777777777777777rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":[],\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"section_a6ae4774a\":{\"options\":{},\"layout\":{\"data-column-mode-sm\":\"single\",\"data-column-mode-xs\":\"single\",\"data-justify\":\"center\"},\"customHeight\":{\"xl\":{\"height\":\"15rem\"}},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"4.444444444444445rem\"},\"xs\":{\"padding-top\":\"3.888888888888889rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"column_0bdc9e6a0\":{\"width\":{\"xl\":\"10\"},\"options\":{},\"layout\":{},\"styles\":{\"xl\":{\"padding-top\":\"0rem\"}},\"motions\":{\"active\":{},\"start\":{},\"end\":{}}},\"content_297ad95af\":{\"content\":{\"xl\":\"<p style=\\\"font-size: 1.27778rem; line-height: 1.66667rem;\\\" data