VALUES
	(1,16,'descricao','<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We adapt to the new paradigms of communication, and we know that simply sending massified press releases is in the past.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Our expertise in creating striking stories, developing a targeted approach to the media and experience in the investment sector gives us an ability to keep track of all the issues related to the communication of a company.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Whether there’s news or not, at The Square we proactively create stories and approaches using methodologies to dialogue with the media, with the goal of generating relevant content to create leads, while adding value to the news production ecosystem.</span>'),
