	(4,16,'_shape','field_5e9b3b2b70414'),
	(5,17,'descricao','Digital influencers can be crucial to give visibility to many brands. They give more personality and develop interesting written and visual content that allows to engage with the public. With so many options to consume information brands need to open new channels of communication to reach relevant audiences.\r\n\r\nAt The Square, we identify the right influencers and build strong relationships with them, considering the goals and values of the brands we work with.'),
